  "comment": "Lotus Light ST 100 PiXEL: The ST-100 is a versatile and powerful lighting solution designed for both\nlarge stages and various environments. With its Outdoor IP65 rating, it ensures\ndurability and reliability even in challenging weather conditions. Featuring\nColor + White Strobe functionality, it delivers dynamic strobe and wash effects,\nperfect for creating vibrant lighting displays and stunning color washes.\nThe ST-100 Aqua excels in effect and painting applications, making it an ideal\nchoice for creating impressive visuals in any setting. While it also delivers\nexcellent results in face lighting. Whether for professional setups or camera\nshots, the ST-100 Aqua performs beautifully.\nThanks to its RDM capability, you can control channels directly from the\nlighting desk, allowing seamless integration into your lighting control system.\nAdditionally, it offers the flexibility to create stunning effects such as 32+16\nsections of horse racing, dyeing, and explosive flashing effects, providing\nendless creative possibilities.",
